params.sqlcmd: "INSERT INTO " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS(\\"ONEROUS_CONS_NO\\", \\"COMPANY_CD\\", \\"VEND_CD\\", \\"PLANT_CD\\", \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", \\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"ISSUE_DATE\\", \\"ISSUE_QTY\\", \\"UNIT_COST\\", \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\", \\"ONEROUS_CONS_COMMENT\\", \\"VEND_LOT_NO\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_CTRL_CD\\", \\"WORK_ODR_CD\\", \\"WORK_IN_PROC_CD\\", \\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\", \\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\", \\"RETURNED_WH_CD\\", \\"RETURNED_CAUSE_CD\\", \\"RETURNED_GNR_TYP\\", \\"AP_PROC_TYP\\", \\"LOT_NO\\") " +"VALUES " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?), ?, TO_DATE(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), ?) " +""

"SELECT " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ONEROUS_CONS_NO\\" AS \\"ONEROUS_CONS_NO\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" AS \\"COMPANY_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"VEND_CD\\" AS \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_ANAME\\" AS \\"VEND_ANAME\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_VEND_CTRL.\\"ROUND_TYP\\") AS \\"ROUND_TYP\\", " +" M_CUR.\\"CUR_UNIT\\" as \\"CUR_UNIT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_CUR.\\"DECIMAL_FIG\\") as \\"DECIMAL_FIG\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"PLANT_CD\\" AS \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" AS \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", " +" TO_NUMBER(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\") AS \\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" AS \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ISSUE_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS \\"ISSUE_DATE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ISSUE_QTY\\") AS \\"ISSUE_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"UNIT_COST\\") AS \\"UNIT_COST\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\") AS \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ONEROUS_CONS_COMMENT\\" AS \\"ONEROUS_CONS_COMMENT\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"LOT_NO\\" AS \\"LOT_NO\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"VEND_LOT_NO\\" AS \\"VEND_LOT_NO\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"RCV_ISSUE_CTRL_CD\\" AS \\"RCV_ISSUE_CTRL_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"WORK_ODR_CD\\" AS \\"WORK_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"WORK_IN_PROC_CD\\" AS \\"WORK_IN_PROC_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" AS \\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\" AS \\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"RETURNED_WH_CD\\" AS \\"RETURNED_WH_CD\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_NAME\\" AS \\"WH_NAME\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"RETURNED_CAUSE_CD\\" AS \\"RETURNED_CAUSE_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"RETURNED_GNR_TYP\\") AS \\"RETURNED_GNR_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"AP_PROC_TYP\\") AS \\"AP_PROC_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\") AS \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" AS \\"STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" M_ITEM.LOT_CTRL_FLG AS \\"LOT_CTRL_FLG\\", " +" M_ITEM.LOT_NUMBERING_TYP AS \\"LOT_NUMBERING_TYP\\" " +"FROM " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_VEND_CTRL, " +" M_WH, " +" M_CUR, " +" SYS_HOME_CUR " +"WHERE " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\"(+) " +" AND T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = M_VEND_CTRL.\\"COMPANY_CD\\"(+) " +" AND T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"VEND_CD\\" = M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\"(+) " +" AND T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"RETURNED_WH_CD\\" = M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\"(+) " +" AND M_CUR.CUR_CD = NVL(M_VEND_CTRL.CUR_CD, SYS_HOME_CUR.HOME_CUR_CD) " +" AND SYS_HOME_CUR.CTRL_CD = 'SYSTEM' " +" AND T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ONEROUS_CONS_NO\\" = ? " +""

"UPDATE " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS " +"SET " +" \\"ISSUE_DATE\\" = TO_DATE(?), " +" \\"ISSUE_QTY\\" = TO_CHAR(?), " +" \\"UNIT_COST\\" = TO_CHAR(?), " +" \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\" = TO_CHAR(?), " +" \\"ONEROUS_CONS_COMMENT\\" = ?, " +" \\"VEND_LOT_NO\\" = ?, " +" \\"RCV_ISSUE_CTRL_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"RETURNED_WH_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"RETURNED_CAUSE_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"LOT_NO\\"=? " +"WHERE " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ONEROUS_CONS_NO\\" = ?"
"DELETE FROM " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS " +"WHERE " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ONEROUS_CONS_NO\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(THIS_MONTH, 'YYYY/MM'), 'YYYY/MM') AS THIS_MONTH " +"FROM " +" SYS_DEBT_CTRL " +"WHERE " +" COMPANY_CD = ( " +" SELECT " +" COMPANY_CD " +" FROM " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +" WHERE " +" CTRL_CD = 'SYSTEM' " +" )"
"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(INSTALL_FLG) AS INSTALL_FLG " +"FROM " +" SYS_INSTALL_OPTIONS " +"WHERE " +" OPTION_ID = 'C*'"
"SELECT " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_ANAME\\" AS \\"VEND_ANAME\\" " +"FROM " +" M_VEND_CTRL " +"WHERE " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" AS \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" AS \\"STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_ITEM.\\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\") AS \\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_ITEM.\\"SPL_ITEM_TYP\\") AS \\"SPL_ITEM_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_ITEM.\\"PRODUCT_TYP\\") AS \\"PRODUCT_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"CLASIFICATION_CD\\" AS \\"CLASIFICATION_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.LOT_CTRL_FLG AS \\"LOT_CTRL_FLG\\", " +" M_ITEM.LOT_NUMBERING_TYP AS \\"LOT_NUMBERING_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" as \\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" " +"FROM " +" M_ITEM " +"WHERE " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"
"SELECT " +" T_ACPT_RSLT.\\"PLANT_CD\\" AS \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" T_ACPT_RSLT " +"WHERE " +" T_ACPT_RSLT.PUCH_ODR_CD = ?"

"SELECT " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.\\"VEND_CD\\" AS \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.\\"ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" T_OD.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" AS \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_ACPT_RSLT.\\"WH_CD\\" AS \\"WH_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ACPT_RSLT.\\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\") AS \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ACPT_RSLT.\\"UNIT_COST\\") AS \\"UNIT_COST\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ACPT_RSLT.\\"PROCESSING_COST\\") AS \\"PROCESSING_COST\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ACPT_RSLT.\\"MATERIAL_COST\\") AS \\"MATERIAL_COST\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ACPT_RSLT.\\"OTHER_OVERHEADS\\") AS \\"OTHER_OVERHEADS\\" " +"FROM " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR, " +" T_OD, " +" T_ACPT_RSLT " +"WHERE " +" T_ACPT_RSLT.PUCH_ODR_CD = T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.PUCH_ODR_CD(+) " +" AND T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.OD_NO = T_OD.OD_NO(+) " +" AND T_ACPT_RSLT.PUCH_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND T_ACPT_RSLT.ACPT_NO = ( " +" SELECT " +" MAX(T_ACPT_RSLT.ACPT_NO) " +" FROM " +" T_ACPT_RSLT " +" WHERE " +" T_ACPT_RSLT.PUCH_ODR_CD = ? " +" )"

"SELECT " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.\\"VEND_CD\\" AS \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.\\"ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" T_OD.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" AS \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR, " +" T_OD " +"WHERE " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.\\"OD_NO\\" = T_OD.\\"OD_NO\\" " +" AND T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" = ?"
"SELECT " +" T_JOB_ODR.\\"PLANT_CD\\" AS \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR " +"WHERE " +" T_JOB_ODR.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(M_PUCH_UNIT_COST.\\"UNIT_COST\\") AS \\"UNIT_COST\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PUCH_UNIT_COST.\\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\") AS \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PUCH_UNIT_COST.\\"PROCESSING_COST\\") AS \\"PROCESSING_COST\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PUCH_UNIT_COST.\\"MATERIAL_COST\\") AS \\"MATERIAL_COST\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PUCH_UNIT_COST.\\"OTHER_OVERHEADS\\") AS \\"OTHER_OVERHEADS\\" " +"FROM " +" M_PUCH_UNIT_COST " +"WHERE " +" M_PUCH_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PUCH_UNIT_COST.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PUCH_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_PUCH_UNIT_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" AS \\"WH_CD\\", " +" M_WH.\\"PLANT_CD\\" AS \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_WH.\\"MRP_FLG\\") AS \\"MRP_FLG\\" " +"FROM " +" M_WH " +"WHERE " +" M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_WH.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_WH.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" AS \\"COMPANY_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"VEND_CD\\" AS \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"PLANT_CD\\" AS \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" AS \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" AS \\"STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_ITEM.\\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\") AS \\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ISSUE_QTY\\") AS \\"ISSUE_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"UNIT_COST\\") AS \\"UNIT_COST\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\") AS \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\" " +"FROM " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS, " +" M_ITEM " +"WHERE " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\"(+) " +" AND T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +""
"SELECT " +" SYS_PARAMETER.\\"VALUE\\" AS \\"VALUE\\" " +"FROM " +" SYS_PARAMETER " +"WHERE " +" SYS_PARAMETER.\\"NAME\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" AS \\"COMPANY_CD\\", " +" M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"VEND_CD\\" AS \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" AS \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS \\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"UNIT_COST\\") AS \\"UNIT_COST\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\") AS \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"ONEROUS_FLG\\") AS \\"ONEROUS_FLG\\" " +"FROM " +" M_CONS_UNIT_COST " +"WHERE " +" M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_CONS_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"INSERT INTO " +" T_ITEM_STOCK(\\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"WH_CD\\", \\"PLANT_CD\\", \\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\", \\"DEFECT_QTY\\", \\"PRVS_DAYEND_STOCK_QTY\\", \\"PRVS_MONTHEND_STOCK_QTY\\", \\"PRVS_TERMEND_STOCK_QTY\\") " +"VALUES " +" (?, ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?), 0, 0, 0, 0)"
"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\") AS \\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\" " +"FROM " +" T_ITEM_STOCK " +"WHERE " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" = ?"
"UPDATE " +" T_ITEM_STOCK " +"SET " +" \\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\" = TO_NUMBER(?) " +"WHERE " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" = ?"
"INSERT INTO " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK(\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", \\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"WH_CD\\", \\"PLANT_CD\\", \\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\") " +"VALUES " +" (?, 0, ?, ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?))"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\") AS \\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\" " +"FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK " +"WHERE " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\" = 0 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" = ?"

"UPDATE " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK " +"SET " +" \\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\" = TO_NUMBER(?) " +"WHERE " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\" = 0 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" = ?"

"INSERT INTO " +" T_RCV_ISSUE(\\"RCV_ISSUE_CTRL_CD\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_TYP\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"PLANT_CD\\", \\"WH_CD\\", \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", \\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\", \\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\", \\"ACPT_NO\\", \\"ACPT_RSLT_CRCT_NO\\", \\"INSPEC_RSLT_CRCT_NO\\", \\"WORK_ODR_CD\\", \\"WORK_IN_PROC_CD\\", \\"PARTIAL_PRD_NO\\", \\"OPR_RSLT_CRCT_NO\\", \\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_BEFORE_QTY\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_QTY\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_AFTER_QTY\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_AMOUNT\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_DATE\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_GNR_TYP\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_ODD_QTY\\", \\"DEFECT_CAUSE_CD\\", \\"STOCK_UPD_TYP\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG\\", \\"OD_NO\\", \\"VEND_LOT_NO\\", \\"RCV_ISSUE_COMMENT\\", \\"COMPANY_CD\\", \\"VEND_CD\\", \\"CONS_TYP\\", \\"CONS_EXEC_DATE\\", \\"LOT_NO\\") " +"VALUES " +" (?, TO_NUMBER(?), ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?), null, TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), null, null, TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), null, TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_DATE(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), null, TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), null, ?, null, ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?), null, ?)"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\") AS \\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\" " +"FROM " +" T_ITEM_STOCK, " +" M_WH, " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"WHERE " +" T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_ITEM_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" = M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\"(+) " +" AND SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"CTRL_CD\\" = 'SYSTEM' " +" AND M_WH.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"COMPANY_CD\\"(+) " +" AND M_WH.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_WH.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" TO_CHAR(T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\") AS \\"STOCK_ON_HAND_QTY\\" " +"FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK, " +" M_WH, " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"WHERE " +" T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\" = 0 " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_JOB_ODR_CD_STOCK.\\"WH_CD\\" = M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\"(+) " +" AND SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"CTRL_CD\\" = 'SYSTEM' " +" AND M_WH.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"COMPANY_CD\\"(+) " +" AND M_WH.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_WH.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ONEROUS_CONS_NO\\" AS \\"ONEROUS_CONS_NO\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" AS \\"COMPANY_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"VEND_CD\\" AS \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"PLANT_CD\\" AS \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" AS \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\") AS \\"JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ISSUE_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS \\"ISSUE_DATE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ISSUE_QTY\\") AS \\"ISSUE_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"UNIT_COST\\") AS \\"UNIT_COST\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\") AS \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ONEROUS_CONS_COMMENT\\" AS \\"ONEROUS_CONS_COMMENT\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"VEND_LOT_NO\\" AS \\"VEND_LOT_NO\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"RCV_ISSUE_CTRL_CD\\" AS \\"RCV_ISSUE_CTRL_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"WORK_ODR_CD\\" AS \\"WORK_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"WORK_IN_PROC_CD\\" AS \\"WORK_IN_PROC_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" AS \\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\" AS \\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"RETURNED_WH_CD\\" AS \\"RETURNED_WH_CD\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"RETURNED_CAUSE_CD\\" AS \\"RETURNED_CAUSE_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"RETURNED_GNR_TYP\\") AS \\"RETURNED_GNR_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"AP_PROC_TYP\\") AS \\"AP_PROC_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\") AS \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.LOT_NO AS \\"LOT_NO\\" " +"FROM " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS " +"WHERE " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ONEROUS_CONS_NO\\" = ? " +"FOR UPDATE NOWAIT"

"UPDATE " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS " +"SET " +" \\"ISSUE_DATE\\" = TO_DATE(?), " +" \\"ISSUE_QTY\\" = TO_CHAR(?), " +" \\"UNIT_COST\\" = TO_CHAR(?), " +" \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\" = TO_CHAR(?), " +" \\"ONEROUS_CONS_COMMENT\\" = ?, " +" \\"VEND_LOT_NO\\" = ?, " +" \\"RETURNED_WH_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"RETURNED_CAUSE_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"LOT_NO\\" = ? " +"WHERE " +" T_PAST_ONEROUS_CONS.\\"ONEROUS_CONS_NO\\" = ?"
